01:23:23.679 --> 01:23:24.870
don't know if you want to stick around

01:23:24.880 --> 01:23:27.110
me, or if we could watch the thing

01:23:27.120 --> 01:23:29.189
together,

01:23:29.199 --> 01:23:30.629
but I'm sure you watch it with your

01:23:30.639 --> 01:23:32.950
kids.

01:23:32.960 --> 01:23:35.750
I didn't want to not have a

01:23:35.760 --> 01:23:37.830
video tonight for you and pray for the

01:23:37.840 --> 01:23:39.350
nation, but it really

01:23:39.360 --> 01:23:40.790
wasn't a lot of prayer; it was me just

01:23:40.800 --> 01:23:43.030
telling you about Jesus coming and about

01:23:43.040 --> 01:23:44.790
the father.

01:23:44.800 --> 01:23:48.070
But

01:23:48.080 --> 01:23:50.950
we love you, and I guess we'll

01:23:50.960 --> 01:23:52.950
end it there.

01:23:57.760 --> 01:23:59.350
I'm sure they want

01:23:59.360 --> 01:24:03.430
to watch him;

01:24:03.440 --> 01:24:06.070
they like watching President Trump. I'm

01:24:06.080 --> 01:24:08.133
curious as to what he's going to say.

01:24:08.143 --> 01:24:11.430
So, to all 5,600 of you, thank

01:24:11.440 --> 01:24:13.430
you for coming out tonight. We love you

01:24:13.440 --> 01:24:16.310
and we'll be back, and we'll pray again,

01:24:16.320 --> 01:24:17.910
praying for the nations

01:24:17.910 --> 01:24:17.920
and

01:24:17.920 --> 01:24:21.510
things to come. Remember to put a smile

01:24:21.520 --> 01:24:24.629
on your face and a song in your heart.

01:24:24.639 --> 01:24:26.790
Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

01:24:26.800 --> 01:24:28.709
God bless you and we'll see you again

01:24:28.719 --> 01:24:31.713
soon. Bye-bye.

